OL,4,C'Ghost school' with no students for a
OL,5,Csecond year
OL,6, For English language schools, the
OL,7, vocabulary that's been most important
OL,8, in recent times has been "empty".
OL,10,FBecause since the pandemic began last
OL,11,Fyear, many language schools have not
OL,12,Fhad any overseas students to teach.
OL,14,FDan Methven, who teaches in the
OL,15,FAnglolang school in Scarborough, says
OL,16,Ffor two summers now they have had a
OL,17,F"ghost school" without students.
OL,19,FEnglish UK, representing language
OL,20,Fschools, says the sector, worth #1.4bn
OL,21,Feach year, is in danger of collapse.
